      <guid isPermaLink="false">bf47742b8426ac3731ca16a445fe55535b4522f7</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 07:16:14 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a44ca6acb019.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f8844bbead.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f729f7bd45.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a44cabf46b10.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a44cace20cd5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f72ad9027e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f72cb416cd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f72da4526d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f7303e6f87.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f7979956fc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f799343002.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f79b003ea4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f7a06b4257.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3f7a249dcc6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Update 1.1.0&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: added subtle stitching to the hat&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: shifted position of lower tunic design&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: added options for less saturated sleeves&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;A very crude attempt to make Link's green tunic not look like pajamas. Intended to work with &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/357421"&gt;Tunic of the Wild Bracers and Sleeve options&lt;/a&gt; by ZeeBuns, however this also works as a standalone, but there won't be sleeves or gloves.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Changes:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Darker Tunic&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Added detail&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Outer tunic has sleeves&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hylian Trousers instead of shorts&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Options:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;  Trousers:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Shorts: Makes no change to the Trousers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Light Trousers: Swaps TotW for Hylian Trousers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dark Trousers: Swaps TotW for Hylian Trousers and switches the default and dark brown dye states&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;Tunic/Cap:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Color Sleeves: The sleeves will be and orange-ish brown&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Brown Sleeves: Sleeves will be a more neutral brown&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Normal Cap: The stripe on the cap is a lighter green&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Yellow Stripe: The stripe on the cap is yellow  &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;NOTE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;For the tunic/cap, only the texture is changed, so don't look too close at the shoulders&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The dark trousers option will affect the default appearance of both the TotW and the actual Hylian Trousers, so if you enable it, you have to dye trousers dark brown to get the original color back&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/wildsetredesign_2af2f.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/wildsetredesign_d918f.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/wildsetredesign_7b74b.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <category>Sets</category>
      <category>Skins</category>
