      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 15:16:57 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3d45a8ea587.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3d45a913cdf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a3d45a933ffc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;QuickFlurryRush UKMM&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;br&gt;Made for UKMM, original by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2176888"&gt;SchuhBaum&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/392663"&gt;Original Mod&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Tested on UKMM v0.17.0-1&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;---&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Reduces the slow motion effect on Link and increases the animation speed during flurry rushes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;ReducedDuration&#13;
 (optional): Link can get at most two attacks with any weapon. The first&#13;
 one is a quick hit and the second one is the flurry rush final attack. &#13;
This option is meant to make flurry rushes less dominating.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;ModifiedDodgeAttackAnimations&#13;
 (optional): Changes attack animations while dodging. For example, &#13;
swords do a normal attack instead of a jump attack. This is meant to &#13;
reduce accidents when failing flurry rushes. Disable this if you run &#13;
into problems with other mods.</description>
