      <guid isPermaLink="false">d95ab6320d02e3407fcc4009ed9c9e6807123d8c</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 19:01:25 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a03b351861e2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a03b35fd360e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a03b3675ff30.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a03b36e485dc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a03b38362e08.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a03b39995143.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a03b3a57fdd1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Sword chemical update&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Added an ice ability to the Ancient Master Sword.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod adds two items to the game: the &lt;b&gt;Ancient Master Sword&lt;/b&gt; and the &lt;b&gt;Ancient Hylian Shield&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Technically, this was intended as a Wii U port of &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1524238"&gt;leeanderthal&lt;/a&gt;'s "&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/246711"&gt;Hero Blight Sword and Shield&lt;/a&gt;" from the Switch, but during the porting process, I started noticing some flaws in the original. So, think of this as a reboot of that mod. Or a remake... Doesn't matter.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I won't list all the features here, but you'll definitely enjoy them as you play :)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod took me much longer than my previous releases... but it was worth it. Thanks to the help from &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1920307"&gt;Nebroc&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1879172"&gt;HGStone&lt;/a&gt;, and Ginger, Queen of Errors (thanks again for the help with texture packing!), I’ve learned a lot, even though less than a month ago I knew absolutely jack shit about BotW modding.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Special thanks&lt;/b&gt; to &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1750563"&gt;i2m&lt;/a&gt; for letting me release this mod using assets from his "&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/428419"&gt;Pink Guardian Sword &amp; Shield&lt;/a&gt;" project.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As for &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1524238"&gt;leeanderthal&lt;/a&gt; - I have no idea how to contact him. His GameBanana profile seems abandoned, and I don't know any of his other socials. So... I figure he won't mind a sort of "restoration" of his mod for the Wii U.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/hyrule_ancient_sheikah_relics.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/hyrule_ancient_sheikah_relics_v1_1.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
