;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;standalone&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;and purchasable in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Akkala Ancient Tech Lab oven&lt;/b&gt;: it has&amp;nbsp;better physics,&amp;nbsp;new heeled sandals, a custom belt and optional pale pink nails.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Setup&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;Install with BCML only one of the available files:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;linkle_old_outfit_nails_v3.bnp:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; The outfit, with &lt;b&gt;pale pink nails&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;linkle_old_outfit_nails_v3__hands.bnp:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Skin color&lt;/b&gt; included for people with grayed arms issue.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;linkle_old_outfit_NO_nails_v3.bnp:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; The outfit, with &lt;b&gt;regular nails&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;linkle_old_outfit_NO_nails_v3__hands.bnp:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Skin color&lt;/b&gt; included for people with grayed arms issue.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Other mods of mine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;ul type="square"&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Stylish Linkle (makeup, earrings, glasses)&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/331562"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the newest Girly Animation Pack&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/49763"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(several options).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Clear Camera UI&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/296638"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(used to get the screenshots).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Linkle mod with a different hairstyle&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/356075"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ko-Fi:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;https://ko-fi.com/i2mods&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;You can&amp;nbsp;support my works by buying me a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;?&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;coffee&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;:)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
