      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632b750416174.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0dfbfb1e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0e2ac89e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0e536c05.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0e7ded9b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0eaa11c0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0ed0f38d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0ef920f7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0f2ac29d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0f5f15e0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0f918897.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0fba17ba.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af0fdc1cd3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af10037e3c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af10291e85.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af1053b1af.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af108ca634.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af10c35adb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af10f20bb5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af11257199.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632af1151ff81.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632e2a8d5d83b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632e2a9083478.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/632e2a937377b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Small fixes&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dress with the skin color included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreyColor"&gt; Alternative versions of the dress with the Linkle skin&lt;br&gt;color included, for those who get grayish hands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hairstyles version 4&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreyColor"&gt;Fixed the blue color on the hair clips.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;INTRODUCTION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;This mod adds as standalone purchasable item in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Akkala Ancient Tech Lab&lt;/b&gt;, a variation of the &lt;b&gt;Travel Outfit&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;used by the &lt;b&gt;Princess Zelda&lt;/b&gt; in the game cutscenes, but specially tailored for &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Linkle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can &lt;b&gt;upgrade&lt;/b&gt; it and also &lt;b&gt;dye it&lt;/b&gt; to get not only several colors, but also &lt;b&gt;different styles&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;With or without &lt;u&gt;skirt&lt;/u&gt;,&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With &lt;u&gt;leggings&lt;/u&gt; or&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; With &lt;u&gt;shorts&lt;/u&gt; (with or without high tights).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;The Princess Zelda &lt;b&gt;long &lt;/b&gt;and &lt;b&gt;short hairstyles&lt;/b&gt;, are also available in a &lt;b&gt;separate mod&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;SETUP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;Install with BCML one of the available files:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;Zelda_Outfit_and_Heels_v3.bnp:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; The outfit, with &lt;b&gt;heeled boots&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;Zelda_Outfit_and_Heels_v3_hands.bnp:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;b&gt;Skin color&lt;/b&gt; included for people with grayed hands issue.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Zelda_Outfit_NO_Heels_v3.bnp:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; The outfit, with &lt;b&gt;plain boots&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Zelda_Outfit_NO_Heels_v3_hands.bnp:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Skin color&lt;/b&gt; included for people with grayed hands issue.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Install with BCML this one too to get the hairstyles:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Zelda_Hairstyles_v4.bnp:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;b&gt;Long&lt;/b&gt; and &lt;b&gt;short&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;hairstyles.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;THANKS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;To &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1739516"&gt;Sockpoppet&lt;/a&gt; for letting me use his version of the &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/321669"&gt;Zelda Champion Triforce&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;as a base for my mod, and his help on&amp;nbsp;properly&amp;nbsp;setting up the hairstyles.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;OTHER MODS OF MINE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;ul type="square"&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Stylish Linkle (makeup, earrings, glasses)&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/skins/181455"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the newest Girly Animation Pack&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/49763"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(several options).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Clear Camera UI&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/296638"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(used to get the screenshots).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Linkle mod with a different hairstyle&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/356075"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ko-Fi:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;https://ko-fi.com/i2mods&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;You can&amp;nbsp;support my works by buying me a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;coffee&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;:)&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/zelda_outfit_and_heels_v3.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/zelda_outfit_and_heels_v3_hands.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
