      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a1cc12668802.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/627ed8b3b213d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/627ed8b29a13a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/627ed8b54ce81.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/627ed8b2ded1b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb7c78ae.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb789fc6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb7bf473.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb6dd1bd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6160c11f7e96a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb8019ab.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb7f2ac7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb7cc8fa.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb7332ed.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb7d8747.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb821c5e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6160c10fa7243.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb8242c8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb8295b0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6160c0fbd3655.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb82c2a1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/60a7bbb84ae10.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Final Version 2026&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(255, 94, 157); font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;span class="PurpleColor"&gt;______________________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(255, 94, 157); font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sixth Anniversary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(110, 225, 108); font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Thank you very much for your support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(110, 225, 108); font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;and feedback all this time! ❤ ❤ ❤&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(108, 177, 225); font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;______________________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(108, 177, 225); font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;Changelog:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(255, 234, 0); font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;✔︎&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; The mod has been &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="PurpleColor"&gt;fully remade&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;to fix a nasty bug that crashed the game very often while equipping the armor. &lt;span style="color: rgb(226, 226, 226); font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;span class="GreyColor"&gt;The problem seems addressed on almost all cases, but to be a hundred percent sure just unequip your current armor before equipping this one (and unequip it before switching to another set). Sorry for the inconvenience, but this is the best I can do!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(255, 234, 0); font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;✔︎&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Thanks to everyone for your kind feedback and your patience.&lt;span class="GreyColor"&gt; Right now I'm not modding this game anymore, but this was a thing I wanted to solve, as it was my first attempt to mod an armor, six long years ago. Cheers all!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(108, 177, 225); font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;______________________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(108, 177, 225); font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;Old versions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(255, 234, 0); font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;✔︎ &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;They have been archived, &lt;span class="GreyColor"&gt;but are still available in the downloads section, if anyone is interested.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;INTRODUCTION&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&#13;
&lt;div class="MsoNormal" align="center"&gt;&#13;
&#13;
&lt;hr width="100%" size="1" noshade="" align="center"&gt;&#13;
&#13;
&lt;/div&gt;&#13;
&#13;
Welcome to the&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Pyra Outfit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;from&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Xenoblade 2&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;for &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Linkle 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;and for&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Zelda’s Ballad&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;! You can use it too on Linkle&amp;nbsp;3 but you will need to install first the &lt;i&gt;Unofficial Linkle 3 Patch&lt;/i&gt; or the &lt;i&gt;Girly Animation Pack&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;2026 Final Version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, and has been remade in an effort to &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;solve the&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;crashes &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;most of us got when equipping the armor. Now the problem has been addressed &lt;u&gt;on almost&lt;/u&gt; all cases! To be a hundred percent sure, just think to unequip your current armor before equipping this one (and unequip this armor before switching to another set). Sorry for the inconvenience, but this is the best I can do!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://media1.tenor.com/images/26dca80f4284484b76dc031605059584/tenor.gif" width="50%"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Ko-Fi:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;https://ko-fi.com/i2mods&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;You can&amp;nbsp;support my works by buying me a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;coffee&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;:)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;WHAT TO INSTALL?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&#13;
&lt;div class="MsoNormal" align="center"&gt;&#13;
&#13;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;Please download and install only one mod file for BCML (UKMM should be compatible):&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul type="square"&gt;&#13;
 &lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Linkle_Pyra_Standalone_2026.bnp&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
 &lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Zelda_Pyra_Standalone_2026.bnp&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Purchasable in the &lt;u&gt;Akkala Ancient Lab&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Linkle_Pyra_Replacement_2026.bnp&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Zelda_Pyra_Replacement_2026.bnp&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Replacing the &lt;u&gt;Flamebreaker Set&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
 &lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Flame Blade&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;(optional)&lt;br&gt;&#13;
     &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;The Aegis sword mod is found&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/288153"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;STORY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;The story behind this mod is longer as myself as a BOTW modder: the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/168229"&gt;old&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Pyra outfit is still available over the Salvager set, and my thoughts one year back were:&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;I want this outfit as a Flamebreaker replacement, it makes more sense!&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;The original mod was clearly discontinued, so I started learning until my port over the Flamebreaker set was ready. It missed the hair physics, and I have been unable to port them until now thanks to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/13978"&gt;Sofia’s tutorial&lt;/a&gt;; she enlightened an obscure path, thanks! Now being able to port the physics, I also wanted to rework in the better way possible the Pyra Outfit using my current knowledge, so here we are: the Pyra outfit has received a&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;big 3D design update&lt;/b&gt;, crisp&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;HD textures&lt;/b&gt;, more details than ever with restored&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;normal maps&lt;/b&gt;, and yes, FINALLY the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;hair physics&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;are working on the&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Linkle version&lt;/u&gt;! (&lt;i&gt;sadly, the Zelda's Ballad version refuses to work and I can't solve it&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you want to see the old full changelog, news, notes... I placed them in a PDF available in the downloads section, under the archived link.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;OTHER MODS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Makeup&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b&gt;earrings&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b&gt;glasses&lt;/b&gt; for Linkle -- &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/331562"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Clear Camera UI&lt;/b&gt; to take clean shots -- &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/296638"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Latest &lt;